import React from "react";
import {
  Body,
  CardArticle,
  Container,
  ContainerArticle,
  Header,
  Title,
  Thumbnail,
  TitleArticle,
  Description,
  BodyArticle,
  BodyText,
  CardInfo,
  ContainerEdit,
  Icon,
} from "../styled/Home";
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome";
import { faPencil, faTrash } from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";

export default function HomePage() {
  const dados = [
    {
      id: "1",
      title: "Artigo 1",
      description: "Descicao do artigo 1",
      body: "texto completo do artigo",
      create_at: "",
      thumbnail:
        "https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3762982/atom6-design-squarelogo-1607449561246.png",
    },
    {
      id: "2",
      title: "Artigo 2",
      description: "Descicao do artigo 2",
      body: "texto completo do artigo",
      create_at: "",
      thumbnail:
        "https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3762982/atom6-design-squarelogo-1607449561246.png",
    },
  ];

  return (
    <Container>
      <Header>
        <Title>CRUD</Title>
      </Header>
      <Body>
        <ContainerArticle>
          <CardArticle>
            <Thumbnail src="" />
            <CardInfo>
              <TitleArticle>Title</TitleArticle>
              <Description>Description</Description>
              <BodyArticle>
                <BodyText>body</BodyText>
              </BodyArticle>
            </CardInfo>
            <ContainerEdit>
              <Icon>
                <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPencil} />
              </Icon>
              <Icon>
                <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTrash} />
              </Icon>
            </ContainerEdit>
          </CardArticle>
        </ContainerArticle>
      </Body>
    </Container>
  );
}
